{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Spring/211226-setup/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Woody","author":"Woody","siteUrl":"https://gintooooonic.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"gintooooonic/gintooooonic.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"fe4154b6-c273-5680-8004-c7f309f09df7","excerpt":"김영한님의 ‘스프링 입문 - 코드로 배우는 스프링 부트, 웹 MVC, DB 접근 기술’\n인프런 강의를 들으며 공부하는 내용들을 간단히 정리한다. Spring 프레임워크를 자세히 공부하기보다는,\n이후의 ‘스프링 기본편’ 강의를 듣기 전에\n간단히 프로젝트를 만들어보며 입문하는 것에\n목적이 있다. 개발 환경 세팅 1. IDE 설치 일반적으로 IntelliJ와 Eclipse를 사용하는데,\n최근에는 IntelliJ를 많이 사용한다고 한다.\n편리한 기능이 굉장히 많다고.. 2. JDK 설치 기존에는 JDK…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"spring\"\n        title=\"spring\"\n        src=\"/static/f11e41fcb46e962e898e8816ba02d5f5/c1b63/spring.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f11e41fcb46e962e898e8816ba02d5f5/5a46d/spring.png 300w,\n/static/f11e41fcb46e962e898e8816ba02d5f5/0a47e/spring.png 600w,\n/static/f11e41fcb46e962e898e8816ba02d5f5/c1b63/spring.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color: #888888; font-size: 12px;\">\n  https://spring.io/\n</p>\n<p>김영한님의 <a href=\"https://www.inflearn.com/course/%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81-%EC%9E%85%EB%AC%B8-%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81%EB%B6%80%ED%8A%B8\">‘스프링 입문 - 코드로 배우는 스프링 부트, 웹 MVC, DB 접근 기술’</a>\n인프런 강의를 들으며 공부하는 내용들을 간단히 정리한다.</p>\n<p>Spring 프레임워크를 자세히 공부하기보다는,\n이후의 ‘스프링 기본편’ 강의를 듣기 전에\n간단히 프로젝트를 만들어보며 입문하는 것에\n목적이 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"개발-환경-세팅\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%B8%ED%8C%85\" aria-label=\"개발 환경 세팅 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개발 환경 세팅</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-ide-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-ide-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 ide 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. IDE 설치</h3>\n<p>일반적으로 IntelliJ와 Eclipse를 사용하는데,\n최근에는 IntelliJ를 많이 사용한다고 한다.\n편리한 기능이 굉장히 많다고..</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-jdk-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-jdk-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"2 jdk 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. JDK 설치</h3>\n<p>기존에는 JDK 8을 사용했지만,\n강의에서 권장하는 JDK 11을 설치했다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"프로젝트-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"프로젝트 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로젝트 생성</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://start.spring.io/\">Spring Initializr</a>를\n사용해서 빠르게 프로젝트를 생성할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"spring_initializr\"\n        title=\"spring_initializr\"\n        src=\"/static/ad3da6808d5884a71ab99037d14e14b7/c1b63/spring_initializr.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ad3da6808d5884a71ab99037d14e14b7/5a46d/spring_initializr.png 300w,\n/static/ad3da6808d5884a71ab99037d14e14b7/0a47e/spring_initializr.png 600w,\n/static/ad3da6808d5884a71ab99037d14e14b7/c1b63/spring_initializr.png 1200w,\n/static/ad3da6808d5884a71ab99037d14e14b7/d61c2/spring_initializr.png 1800w,\n/static/ad3da6808d5884a71ab99037d14e14b7/97a96/spring_initializr.png 2400w,\n/static/ad3da6808d5884a71ab99037d14e14b7/c50e3/spring_initializr.png 2442w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Project : Gradle과 Maven이 빌드와 의존성 관리 등을 담당하는 것 같다.\nGradle을 사용하기로.</li>\n<li>Language : Java</li>\n<li>Spring Boot : Spring Boot의 버전을 선택한다.\nSNAPSHOT 버전을 제외한 최신 버전을 선택했다.</li>\n<li>Project Metadata : 프로젝트의 그룹명과 이름 등을 설정한다.\n자바 버전은 11을 사용하도록 설정한다.</li>\n<li>Dependencies : 의존성을 추가할 수 있다. Spring Web과\nThymeleaf을 추가한다. Thymeleaf는 템플릿 엔진이라고 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>하단의 GENERATE를 통해 프로젝트를 다운로드하고 IntelliJ에서 Open한다.\n처음 프로젝트를 열면 잠시동안 의존성 라이브러리가 다운로드된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"프로젝트-구조\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0\" aria-label=\"프로젝트 구조 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로젝트 구조</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 676px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 113.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"project\"\n        title=\"project\"\n        src=\"/static/e8b72e2343eb86085b5ec3fb212a65ea/9bb7a/project.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e8b72e2343eb86085b5ec3fb212a65ea/5a46d/project.png 300w,\n/static/e8b72e2343eb86085b5ec3fb212a65ea/0a47e/project.png 600w,\n/static/e8b72e2343eb86085b5ec3fb212a65ea/9bb7a/project.png 676w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 676px) 100vw, 676px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">.idea</code></td>\n<td>IntelliJ 설정 폴더</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">gradle</code></td>\n<td>gradle 관련 폴더</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">src/main</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">java</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">resources</code> 폴더가 존재하며, <code class=\"language-text\">java</code> 폴더에 패키지와 소스 코드들이 위치함.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">src/test</code></td>\n<td>테스트 코드</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">build.gradle</code></td>\n<td>Gradle 관련 설정 파일. Spring Initializr에 의해 이미 작성되어 있음.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"프로젝트-실행\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-label=\"프로젝트 실행 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로젝트 실행</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">/src/main/java/com.hello.startspring/StartSpringApplication</code>에 위치한\n기본 메인 클래스를 실행한다.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://localhost:8080\">localhost:8080</a> 접속</li>\n<li>Whitelabel Error Page가 출력되면 성공!</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"whitelabel_error\"\n        title=\"whitelabel_error\"\n        src=\"/static/5ae244a258682a417dd2748a6d5c4580/c1b63/whitelabel_error.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5ae244a258682a417dd2748a6d5c4580/5a46d/whitelabel_error.png 300w,\n/static/5ae244a258682a417dd2748a6d5c4580/0a47e/whitelabel_error.png 600w,\n/static/5ae244a258682a417dd2748a6d5c4580/c1b63/whitelabel_error.png 1200w,\n/static/5ae244a258682a417dd2748a6d5c4580/cd138/whitelabel_error.png 1220w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"기타-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"기타 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기타 설정</h2>\n<h3 id=\"project-탭-패키지-표시-방식-변경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#project-%ED%83%AD-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80-%ED%91%9C%EC%8B%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"project 탭 패키지 표시 방식 변경 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Project 탭 패키지 표시 방식 변경</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"project_view\"\n        title=\"project_view\"\n        src=\"/static/9fe7a60d39a5883f8d18126a1f111150/c1b63/project_view.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9fe7a60d39a5883f8d18126a1f111150/5a46d/project_view.png 300w,\n/static/9fe7a60d39a5883f8d18126a1f111150/0a47e/project_view.png 600w,\n/static/9fe7a60d39a5883f8d18126a1f111150/c1b63/project_view.png 1200w,\n/static/9fe7a60d39a5883f8d18126a1f111150/b1ffc/project_view.png 1492w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n[Project 탭의 설정 아이콘] > [Tree Appearance] > [Compact Middle Packages] 설정을 통해\n패키지 구조를 다르게 띄울 수 있다. (패키지 이름을 나누지 않고 한번에 보여줄 것인지의 여부)</p>\n<h3 id=\"프로젝트-실행-방식-변경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"프로젝트 실행 방식 변경 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로젝트 실행 방식 변경</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"run_settings\"\n        title=\"run_settings\"\n        src=\"/static/1960db73d0c746fb1fd3a7ba9da2be67/c1b63/run_settings.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1960db73d0c746fb1fd3a7ba9da2be67/5a46d/run_settings.png 300w,\n/static/1960db73d0c746fb1fd3a7ba9da2be67/0a47e/run_settings.png 600w,\n/static/1960db73d0c746fb1fd3a7ba9da2be67/c1b63/run_settings.png 1200w,\n/static/1960db73d0c746fb1fd3a7ba9da2be67/d61c2/run_settings.png 1800w,\n/static/1960db73d0c746fb1fd3a7ba9da2be67/912fc/run_settings.png 1934w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>프로젝트를 Gradle로 실행하는 것이 기본 설정인데,\n자바로 직접 실행하는 것보다 느리다고 한다.</p>\n<p>[Preferences] > [Build, Execution, Deployment] > [Build Tools] > [Gradle]\n에서 [Build and run using]과 [Run tests using] 항목을 IntelliJ IDEA로 설정한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inflearn.com/course/%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81-%EC%9E%85%EB%AC%B8-%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81%EB%B6%80%ED%8A%B8\">김영한, 스프링 입문 - 코드로 배우는 스프링 부트, 웹 MVC, DB 접근 기술</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/Spring/211226-setup/#%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%B8%ED%8C%85\">개발 환경 세팅</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211226-setup/#1-ide-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">1. IDE 설치</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211226-setup/#2-jdk-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">2. JDK 설치</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211226-setup/#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">프로젝트 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211226-setup/#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0\">프로젝트 구조</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211226-setup/#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\">프로젝트 실행</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/Spring/211226-setup/#%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">기타 설정</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211226-setup/#project-%ED%83%AD-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80-%ED%91%9C%EC%8B%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD\">